How To Install

1. Unpack and install.  Do not start prog.
2.Transfer runme.bat to the installed folder
3.Run runme.bet in installed folder.A  window for the username  and password will appear.
4.Use the key generator to generate a valid serial.
5.Use the  info generated  for the window in step 3. Done.
Do not use register from the pc tools app.
